{"tid":1851091,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[i/a] 阿爾克戰記 madhead新game","createTime":"2020-01-30T01:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:46:34.000Z","uid":38604,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0f0a522aca7132e5afa4aa1782f52a1a8b905d","tid":1851091,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:39:39.000Z","msg":"Madhead全新作品《Arcane Revelation 阿爾克戰記》是一款集合了「生存、競速、死鬥」，以射擊決勝負的手機遊戲！只需簡單的操作就能享受刺激爽快戰鬥，考驗你的眼界、技術和反應！馬上號召身邊所有朋友來投身戰場吧！<br />\n【2 人組隊協力共鬥】<br />\n玩家組成 2 人隊伍，合力奪取石板，然後脫離迷宮，最快者為勝！<br />\n【爭奪資源弱肉強食】<br />\n在地圖上擊殺魔物收集資源進行升級，手腳太慢只有死路一條！<br />\n【戰鬥方法隨你風格】<br />\n你可以善用地形進行回避及隱匿，偷襲對手；亦可以與隊友堂堂正正地與敵人開戰！<br />\n【培育角色制霸戰場】<br />\n10個角色各有風格，獲取裝備可以進行強化，令戰鬥變得有利！<br />\n【創建團隊結伴暢玩】<br />\n創立「探險隊」並廣邀各路玩家加入，分享戰術和團練！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家封測緊，每逢夜晚18-24點開放玩，有冇爸打有code share<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80713a603fb72e740eff8d11448d63a7ad8ea9b8","tid":1851091,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"留名等睇今次幾時執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256878885e8bcf062f4e8f95d45cf005e2502b8e","tid":1851091,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"今次係競技game, 應該挨到一年嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bde462cc09960649d24f346ef305096185b1d2","tid":1851091,"uid":29513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"抄完pad 再抄埋brawl stars<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d40a896913be72b2c54fdf6954000b676281ff","tid":1851091,"uid":29932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"好似幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2275109a7f9a4d4d3a71b9ec7953eddc50dc10","tid":1851091,"uid":45694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"